# Data Layer Architecture (v2)

## PostgreSQL

- Migrations: database/migrations/NNN_name.sql
- Tenant tables: tenant_id + indexes; soft delete via deleted_at + deleted_by

## v2 Tables (launch scope)

- accounting_periods.status includes locked
- document_metadata (R2 storage_key)
- sync_queue + change_log (LWW sync)
- analytics_snapshots (dashboard KPIs)

## Shared Packages (edit here, not backend copies)

| Source | Backend copy |
|--------|----------------|
| shared/financial-core/ | backend/src/financial/ (AUTO-GENERATED) |
| shared/report-engines/ | backend/dist/*.mjs via ensure-*-engine.mjs (transitional) |
| shared/rbac/permissions.ts | backend/src/auth/permissions.ts |

Regenerate: npm run build:backend

## SQLite (local-only)

services/database/schema.ts → npm run electron:extract-schema → electron/schema.sql

## New Report

1. Engine in shared/report-engines/ (no React)
2. ReportService + route under /api/v1/reports/
3. RBAC permission in shared/rbac/

Full guide: doc/ARCHITECTURE.md §4.
